snippet.title: The Danish Girl Official Movie Review
snippet.description:
The Danish Girl starring Eddie Redmayne, Alicia Vikander, and Amber Heard is reviewed by Christy Lemire (http://www.ChristyLemire.com), Scott Mantz (Movie Mantz, Access Hollywood), and Tim Grierson (Screen International)

See what other critics are saying: http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_danish_girl_2015/

The remarkable love story inspired by the lives of artists Lili Elbe and Gerda Wegener. Lili and Gerda's marriage and work evolve as they navigate Lili's groundbreaking journey as a transgender pioneer. -- (C) Focus Features

Watch more movie reviews: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLm4XLke0iGptnCMraDr39laDOUbpEUins
